@Node "Introduction"

  @{b}Introduction@{ub}


    The library is a set of function to manipulate
    workbench.library V44 (AmigaOS 3.5) or higher.

@EndNode

@Node "Author" "RxWB Author"

  @{b}Author@{ub}


    I am @{i}Alfonso Ranieri@{ui}

    My e-mail address is @{i}alforan@tin.it@{ui}

    You can find last version of this library at my home page:
    @{i}http://digilander.libero.it/asoft/@{ui}

@EndNode

