@Node "Functions" "RxWB Functions"

  @{b}Functions@{ub}


    Any function may also be called as RXWB_FunctionName and
    RXWBFunctionName to avoid conflicts with other libraries.

    Note that AppIcon and Icon manipulation functions are also
    included in rmh.library.

    Icons manipulation      AppIcon
    @{" WBAskToolType     " LINK "WBAskToolType"            }    @{" WBAddAppIcon      " LINK "WBAddAppIcon"             }
    @{" WBGetIconAttrs    " LINK "WBGetIconAttrs"           }    @{" WBGetToolType     " LINK "WBGetToolType"            }
    @{" WBAppIconSignal   " LINK "WBAppIconSignal"          }    @{" WBPutToolType     " LINK "WBPutToolType"            }
    @{" WBFreeAppIcon     " LINK "WBFreeAppIcon"            }    @{" WBReadToolTypes   " LINK "WBReadToolTypes"          }
    @{" WBHandleAppIcon   " LINK "WBHandleAppIcon"          }    @{" WBWriteToolTypes  " LINK "WBWriteToolTypes"         }

    Workbench               Various
    @{" WBChangeSelection " LINK "WBChangeSelection"        }    @{" Help              " LINK "Help"                     }
    @{" WBCloseObject     " LINK "WBCloseObject"            }
    @{" WBGetAttr         " LINK "WBGetAttr"                }
